# Lichess API token for chess-self-coach (used to fetch your games)
#
# How to create:
#   1. Go to https://lichess.org/account/oauth/token/create
#   2. Token description: chess-self-coach
#   3. No special scopes needed (default permissions are sufficient)
#   4. Click Submit — copy the token (shown only once, starts with lip_)
#
# To test your token manually:
#   curl -H "Authorization: Bearer lip_your_token" https://lichess.org/api/account
#
LICHESS_API_TOKEN=lip_your_token_here
